{
  "stem": "4113.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Now, my cousin was a different story.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Although they were Orthodox too, the kids were rebellious.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he was a rebel.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he had friends among the gentile kids.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he would, as a matter of fact, gang up on kids, who, for example, on the Sabbath when the Jews used to come back from the synagogue, and some kids would throw stones at them, he would gang up and hide.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And if he caught these kids, would beat the heck out of them.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he had gentile kids that were with him.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They were his buddy buddies, so they would all-- he would remember who it was who threw the stones.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they would gang up, and then, beat that kid up awfully.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He was a rebel, and even is a rebel now.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "His own kids tell the story that he walks around with a gun.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "He has a gun at home.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And he is a member of the gun club.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "You know, and he has also gentile friends who are gun club members.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But he was a different sort of a story than myself.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I was religious.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And although they were religious as well, they would, for example, hide and buy some non-kosher sausages or send in a friend to buy them non-kosher sausages.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Or they would smoke on the Sabbath, you know, hide somewhere so that no one will see them.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And that wasn't the case with our family.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Mark Frooman.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He lives in Manchester.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He was just in New York to a wedding.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we had met there again.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] as comfortable as you could.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There were some kids, you know, who were, you know, anti-Semitic.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know, they learned it at home.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
